Step 1: Login to Salesforce
1. Open Browser
Open Google Chrome
2. Go to Salesforce
Type in search bar:
https://login.salesforce.com
Press Enter
3. Login
Enter:
•	Username 
•	Password 
Click:
Log In
________________________________________
Step 2: Switch to Lightning Experience
After login, check top-right corner.
If you see:
Switch to Lightning Experience
Click it.
(If already in Lightning mode, skip this step)
________________________________________
Step 3: Open Object Manager
At top right click:
⚙️ Setup (Gear Icon)
Then click:
Setup
A new page opens.
At top, click:
Object Manager
________________________________________
Step 4: Create Custom Object
Click:
Create → Custom Object
Now fill details:
Object Label:
Type:
Student Detail
Plural Label:
Type:
Student Details
Object Name:
It fills automatically.
________________________________________
Step 5: Select Optional Features
Tick these options:
✅ Allow Reports
✅ Allow Activities
Leave other options default.
Click:
Save
________________________________________
