Step 18: Copy URL
After record opens
Go to browser top address bar
Copy the full URL
Shortcut:
Ctrl + C
________________________________________
Step 19: Open Developer Tools
Open new Chrome tab
Shortcut:
Ctrl + T
Then click:
⋮ (3 dots top-right)
Go to:
More Tools → Developer Tools
OR directly press:
Ctrl + Shift + I
________________________________________
Step 20: Paste URL
Inside Developer Tools use required section (usually Console)
Paste copied URL:
Ctrl + V
