Easy Remember Flow
1.
Login Salesforce
2.
Setup → Object Manager → Create Custom Object
3.
Add Fields
•	Email 
•	Phone 
•	Date of Birth 
4.
Create Tab
5.
App Manager → New Lightning App
6.
Add Student Detail in Navigation
7.
Open App
8.
Create Student Record
9.
Copy URL
10.
Chrome → Developer Tools → Paste URL
That’s the complete practical in simple steps.

